OL,3,CNew research reveals harsh financial
OL,4,Crealities of student loans controversy
OL,6,FA new survey for ITV News shows that
OL,7,Faround two thirds of student loan
OL,8,Fborrowers who responded have seen
OL,9,Ftheir debt grow since leaving higher
OL,10,Feducation.
OL,12,FIt comes as the prime minister has
OL,13,Fpromised to look for ways to make
OL,14,Fthings fairer and MPs start a new
OL,15,Finquiry into the controversy.
OL,17,FThe findings are from a survey of
OL,18,Faround 2,500 student loan borrowers -
OL,19,Fall from the controversial scheme
OL,20,Fknown as Part 2.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
