OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1773792182
OL,3,CNew research reveals harsh financial
OL,4,Crealities of student loans controversy
OL,6,FThe research was conducted by Organise
OL,7,Ffor ITV News.
OL,9,FWhen Faith Kanteh graduated in 2023,
OL,10,Fher debt was already more than
OL,11,F#54,000. It's now grown beyond #67,000.
OL,13,FShe said: "(I'm) shocked. Shocked as
OL,14,Fanyone would feel. I think I saw it
OL,15,Fand was like, there's no way that I,
OL,16,Fat 17, 18 years old, signed up for
OL,17,Fthat kind of debt.
OL,26,@uD@LpmuD@Ppn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1773792182
OL,3,CNew research reveals harsh financial
OL,4,Crealities of student loans controversy
OL,6,F"When we were in school, we were
OL,7,Fcategorically told, you won't notice
OL,8,Fthe payments, you won't notice it.
OL,9,FIt's just something in the background
OL,10,Ffor me now.
OL,12,F"I've had to look and move back with
OL,13,Fmy mum because I can't save anything.
OL,14,FI do nothing. I spend on barely
OL,15,Fanything and I've got nothing left."
OL,17,FFaith Kanteh told ITV News she was
OL,18,F"shocked" by how much her debt had
OL,19,Fgrown
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
