OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1773792182
OL,3,CNew research reveals harsh financial
OL,4,Crealities of student loans controversy
OL,6,FAt the centre of growing complaints
OL,7,Fare student loans from 2012 to 2023,
OL,8,Fknown as Plan 2.
OL,10,FBorrowers pay 9% of their income above
OL,11,Fan earnings threshold which will be
OL,12,Fjust over #29,385 from April, but the
OL,13,Fgovernment is freezing that threshold
OL,14,Funtil 2030. The freeze will drag more
OL,15,Fpeople into repayments over time.
OL,17,FAs a former government advisor, Nick
OL,18,FHillman, was a key player in designing
OL,19,Fthese loans in 2012.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1773792182
OL,3,CNew research reveals harsh financial
OL,4,Crealities of student loans controversy
OL,6,FHe said: "A lot of the tweaks that
OL,7,Fhave happened to the student loans
OL,8,Fmean that 100% of the costs of the
OL,9,Feducation are now being paid back by
OL,10,FPlan 2 borrowers.
OL,12,F"Whereas when we designed the system
OL,13,Fback in 2012, it was meant to be more
OL,14,Flike a 40/60 split, you know, with
OL,15,Factually the taxpayer still picking up
OL,16,Fa very significant part of the cost."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
