SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1773792182
OL,3,CNew research reveals harsh financial
OL,4,Crealities of student loans controversy
OL,6,FWhen asked if he feels any sense of
OL,7,Fresponsibility for how it's all turned
OL,8,Fout, he told ITV News that "it's
OL,9,Freally important" that "the government
OL,10,Fdoes something quickly".
OL,12,FHe said: "Year 13 pupils are about to
OL,13,Fgo into the big examination period and
OL,14,Fif they read and hear all the concerns
OL,15,Fabout student finance and that puts
OL,16,Fthem off, then I think that's
OL,17,Fworrying."
OL,19,FFormer government advisor, Nick
OL,20,FHillman, says the government needs to
OL,21,Fact quickly
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
