OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1773792182
OL,3,CNew research reveals harsh financial
OL,4,Crealities of student loans controversy
OL,6,FThis is one of the first surveys to
OL,7,Fget opinions about possible reforms
OL,8,Ffrom the student loan borrowers.
OL,10,F76% say interest rates should be
OL,11,Flowered and 53% want the threshold to
OL,12,Fbe raised.
OL,14,FCritics of the loans claim that, by
OL,15,Ffreezing the repayment threshold,
OL,16,Fgovernment is acting like a loan
OL,17,Fshark, changing terms and conditions
OL,18,Flong after people signed up.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
