CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1773792182
OL,3,CNew research reveals harsh financial
OL,4,Crealities of student loans controversy
OL,6,FBut a spokesperson for the Taxpayers
OL,7,FAlliance says the original agreements
OL,8,Fdid include a warning that government
OL,9,Fpolicies could change.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, the government says it's
OL,12,Fconsidering options for reform.
OL,14,FPatrick Ba-Tin says his debt has grown
OL,15,Fby nearly #20,000 since he graduated
OL,16,Fin 2017
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
