OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1773792182
OL,3,CNew research reveals harsh financial
OL,4,Crealities of student loans controversy
OL,6,FPatrick Ba-Tin graduated in 2017 with
OL,7,Fa debt of more than #41,000, but
OL,8,Fthat's now grown to almost #60,000,
OL,9,Fdespite repaying more than #2,000 a
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FHe said: "I could be paying #200 into
OL,13,Fmy pension every month, or I could be
OL,14,Foverpaying my mortgage #200 a month.
OL,16,F"All of these things are things that
OL,17,Feveryone advises you to do when you're
OL,18,Four age.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
